		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Tide</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about tides in the Earth's oceans.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Tide_(disambiguation)" title="Tide (disambiguation)">Tide (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">"Tidal" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Tidal_(disambiguation)" title="Tidal (disambiguation)">Tidal (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" align="right">
<tr align="center">
<td>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:162px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Bay_of_Fundy_High_Tide.jpg" class="image" title="The Bay of Fundy at high water"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Bay_of_Fundy_High_Tide.jpg/160px-Bay_of_Fundy_High_Tide.jpg" width="160" height="240" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Bay_of_Fundy_High_Tide.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The <a href="/wiki/Bay_of_Fundy" title="Bay of Fundy">Bay of Fundy</a> at high water</div>
</div>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:162px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Bay_of_Fundy_Low_Tide.jpg" class="image" title="The Bay of Fundy at low water"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Bay_of_Fundy_Low_Tide.jpg/160px-Bay_of_Fundy_Low_Tide.jpg" width="160" height="240" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Bay_of_Fundy_Low_Tide.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
