<li id="cite_note-Jain-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Jain_1-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFB.C._Punmia.2C_Ashok_Kumar_Jain.2C_Arun_K_Jain2005">B.C. Punmia, Ashok Kumar Jain, Arun K Jain (2005). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=oT5EeEDrK04C&amp;pg=PA317&amp;vq=equilibrium+theory&amp;dq=isbn=8170080800&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=ACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr_kX7zEQQ" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=oT5EeEDrK04C&amp;pg=PA317&amp;vq=equilibrium+theory&amp;dq=isbn=8170080800&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=ACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr_kX7zEQQ" rel="nofollow">Surveying</a></i> (Vol. 2 ed.). Laxmi Publications. pp.&#160;317. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/8170080800" class="internal">ISBN 8170080800</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=oT5EeEDrK04C&amp;pg=PA317&amp;vq=equilibrium+theory&amp;dq=isbn=8170080800&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=ACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr_kX7zEQQ" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=oT5EeEDrK04C&amp;pg=PA317&amp;vq=equilibrium+theory&amp;dq=isbn=8170080800&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=ACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr_kX7zEQQ" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=oT5EeEDrK04C&amp;pg=PA317&amp;vq=equilibrium+theory&amp;dq=isbn=8170080800&amp;source=gbs_search_s&amp;sig=ACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr_kX7zEQQ</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Surveying&amp;rft.aulast=B.C.+Punmia%2C+Ashok+Kumar+Jain%2C+Arun+K+Jain&amp;rft.au=B.C.+Punmia%2C+Ashok+Kumar+Jain%2C+Arun+K+Jain&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B317&amp;rft.edition=Vol.+2&amp;rft.pub=Laxmi+Publications&amp;rft.isbn=8170080800&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DoT5EeEDrK04C%26pg%3DPA317%26vq%3Dequilibrium%2Btheory%26dq%3Disbn%3D8170080800%26source%3Dgbs_search_s%26sig%3DACfU3U3HeuKZPmGsvbiqDXrkZr