<li id="cite_note-Hubbard-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Hubbard_2-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFRichard_Hubbard1893">Richard Hubbard (1893). <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=nfWSxRr8VP4C&amp;pg=PA54&amp;dq=centrifugal+revolution+and+rotation+date:1970-2009&amp;lr=&amp;as_brr=0&amp;sig=ACfU3U2e_gEEDUG4mB1nO2GS21kCJwUJVQ#PPA54,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=nfWSxRr8VP4C&amp;pg=PA54&amp;dq=centrifugal+revolution+and+rotation+date:1970-2009&amp;lr=&amp;as_brr=0&amp;sig=ACfU3U2e_gEEDUG4mB1nO2GS21kCJwUJVQ#PPA54,M1" rel="nofollow">Boater's Bowditch: The Small Craft American Practical Navigator</a></i>. McGraw-Hill Professional. pp.&#160;54. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0071361367" class="internal">ISBN 0071361367</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/44059064" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/44059064" rel="nofollow">44059064</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=nfWSxRr8VP4C&amp;pg=PA54&amp;dq=centrifugal+revolution+and+rotation+date:1970-2009&amp;lr=&amp;as_brr=0&amp;sig=ACfU3U2e_gEEDUG4mB1nO2GS21kCJwUJVQ#PPA54,M1" class="external free" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=nfWSxRr8VP4C&amp;pg=PA54&amp;dq=centrifugal+revolution+and+rotation+date:1970-2009&amp;lr=&amp;as_brr=0&amp;sig=ACfU3U2e_gEEDUG4mB1nO2GS21kCJwUJVQ#PPA54,M1" rel="nofollow">http://books.google.com/books?id=nfWSxRr8VP4C&amp;pg=PA54&amp;dq=centrifugal+revolution+and+rotation+date:1970-2009&amp;lr=&amp;as_brr=0&amp;sig=ACfU3U2e_gEEDUG4mB1nO2GS21kCJwUJVQ#PPA54,M1</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Boater%27s+Bowditch%3A+The+Small+Craft+American+Practical+Navigator&amp;rft.aulast=Richard+Hubbard&amp;rft.au=Richard+Hubbard&amp;rft.date=1893&amp;rft.pa