<li><a href="http://tidesite.appspot.com/" class="external text" title="http://tidesite.appspot.com/" rel="nofollow">Mapped, graphical US tide tables/charts in calendar form from NOAA data</a></li>
<li><a href="http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/" class="external text" title="http://tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov/" rel="nofollow">National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA)</a></li>
<li><a href="http://easytide.ukho.gov.uk/EasyTide/EasyTide/index.aspx" class="external text" title="http://easytide.ukho.gov.uk/EasyTide/EasyTide/index.aspx" rel="nofollow">UK Admiralty Easytide</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.pol.ac.uk/ntslf/tidalp.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pol.ac.uk/ntslf/tidalp.html" rel="nofollow">UK, South Atlantic, British Overseas Territories and Gibraltar tide times from the UK National Tidal and Sea Level Facility</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.protides.com" class="external text" title="http://www.protides.com" rel="nofollow">US Tide Prediction, mapped with graphical calendars and tabular view</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bcgov.net/bftlib/tides.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.bcgov.net/bftlib/tides.htm" rel="nofollow">Tides: Why They Happen — Beaufort County Library</a></li>
<li><a href="http://tbone.biol.sc.edu/tide/" class="external text" title="http://tbone.biol.sc.edu/tide/" rel="nofollow">WWW Tide and Current Predictor</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mobilegeographics.com:81/" class="external text" title="http://www.mobilegeographics.com:81/" rel="nofollow">XTide Tide Prediction Server</a></li>
</ul>


